Parma-Ham-Horizon-2020

SMART FOOD – Supervised Production And Real-time Traceability in food distribution, represents the winning project for the cascadilly funded Horizon 2020 project.The project will be implemented in the Parma-Ham, the world largest ham producer with more than 50 000 workers.

Lead researches:

  • PhD Dejan Mircetic
  • PhD Marinko Maslaric

Goal: design fully automated AI food factory for purpose of providing agile production & logistic system.
